title: Grateful Dead Live at Berkeley Community Theater on 1986-04-18
description:
Set 1

Alabama Getaway-> Greatest Story Ever Told, West L.A. Fadeaway, CC Rider, Brown Eyed Women, Me & My Uncle-> Mexicali Blues, Tons Of Steel, My Baby Left Me-> That's Alright Mama, The Music Never Stopped

Set 2

Shakedown Street, Women Are Smarter-> He's Gone-> Drums-> The Wheel-> Smokestack Lightning-> Stella Blue-> Around & Around-> Johnny B. Goode, E: U.S. Blues

Rex Benefit

reviews.review_text: 5 stars for sound and being there You did a fantastic job on these 4 nights.Great spot for recording thats for sure. In your faCE loud and clear rite down to the drumming.I had a blast at these shows and now can relive them anyday I want.  THANK you
- Show is kinda stormy & loose, some great licks but not very good navigation by Garcia.
